You're Invited for Shaker`s exclusive launch party
Dustin Moskovitz was invited
We are proud to announce that Sarah Austin will host and greet guests at the door of Temple this Thursday night, 7:53pm to be exact) in SF to celebrate the launch of Shaker. As many of you have started to tweet and talk about, she is cast on the Bravo reality TV show and is documenting her life, part of it as an angel investor in Shaker. Come enjoy live music by FAR EAST MOVEMENT and more.. There's hors d’oeuvres and a hosted bar till 10pm...and, of course, the best company in town. And did we mention there will be surprises? Well...there will be surprises. We perfer the party to stay private and by invite only, hence we decided to keep the Bravo cameras out this time but happy to have Sarah and friends with us.
Thursday, June 7, 2012 at 7:50pm in PDT
Temple SF

Bubble Tank Pitch On National TV
Dustin Moskovitz was invited
Please RSVP and purchase tickets at http://bubbletank.eventbrite.com The Four Seasons, Palo Alto Ballroom Hors d'oeuvres and Drinks Dress: formal business attire meets hollywood On behalf of Sarah Austin and the Pop17 team, I would like to invite you to Pop17's "Bubble Tank" this coming Thursday, July 5th, from 3pm to 6pm at the Four Seasons Silicon Valley. The “Bubble Tank” event is aimed to connect founders to venture capitalists and is going to be filmed by a major TV network. The format will follow that of ABC's "Shark Tank", where CEOs and founders pitch their companies to investors. The event will be a great way to connect and is an opportunity to be seen by millions of viewers. It's $15 online and $20 at the door.
Thursday, July 5, 2012 at 2:30pm in PDT
Four Seasons Hotel Silicon Valley

BlackJet San Francisco Launch Event
Dustin Moskovitz was invited
VALENTINE'S DAY, FEBRUARY 14TH, 2013 NOON-1PM UNION SQUARE PARK $6M Giveaway 1st 1,000 guests to arrive will receive a comped membership + a complimentary companion seat to any BlackJet destination. GRAND PRIZE WINNER: Private Jet Trip to Las Vegas for 2 ~Roundtrip Private Jet Seat service from San Francisco to Las Vegas ~Departs Thursday February 14th @ 6pm. Returns Sunday at 6pm ~3 Nights at the Bellagio, Limo transfers and $1,000 in CASH! Local SF fave DJ David Carvalho will be playing some lunchtime beats, so come on down and get your free membership along with your photo taken in our aviation themed digital photobooth! BlackJet’s San Francisco Launch Event will celebrate their new direct service route connecting San Francisco with Los Angeles, New York, and Las Vegas. Already dubbed the “Uber for Private Jets," BlackJet is an online service and phone app that connects travelers with the reliability and convenience of a private jet experience at commercial prices. BlackJet is backed by Garrett Camp, founding CEO of StumbleUpon and co-founder of Uber, and has an all-star list of investors including Salesforce CEO Marc Benioff, First Round Capital, Shervin Pishevar, SV Angel, Ashton Kutcher, Guy Oseary, Tim Ferriss, Steve Jang and more. The service is currently invite-only, but you can log in to their site with the code forbesvip300.
Thursday, February 14, 2013, 12 PM - 1 PM in PST
Union Square, San Francisco
